						<summary>

						<p>On a broken slab on the tank bund.</p>						

						<p>Circa 10th century.</p>						

						<p>It states that the record was composed by Sāmiyaṇṇa and the inscribed slab was set up by Chāvuṇḍa. Only the last few lines of the epigraph are preserved, the earlier portion having been broken and lost.</p>						

						</summary>
